| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-0748 — Recovery Inhibition (pear)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 5059c5d8-e7a5-57e3-9b8f-44c5167c91ea"
